        <mxCell id="84" value="&lt;span&gt;The cloud adapter sends the&lt;br&gt;corresponding cloud API&lt;br&gt;request to the Cloud Platform&lt;br&gt;Appliance through the cloud&lt;br&gt;API service.&lt;/span&gt;" style="text;html=1;resizable=0;points=[];autosize=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingTop=-4;" parent="1" vertex="1">
