        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="85" value="&lt;span&gt;The Cloud Platform Appliance&lt;br&gt;processes the API request. If it is not&lt;br&gt;authoritative for objects referenced in&lt;br&gt;the request, it proxies the request to&lt;br&gt;the Grid Master or another Cloud&lt;br&gt;Platform Appliance, depending on the&lt;br&gt;authority delegation.&lt;/span&gt;" style="text;html=1;resizable=0;points=[];autosize=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingTop=-4;" parent="1" vertex="1">
